    ],
    "keySignals": [
      "Oil crossing $100 triggers our stagflation threshold, fundamentally altering the macro backdrop from disinflationary relief.",
      "Dollar strength from geopolitical tensions is pressuring all risk assets and emerging market currencies.",
      "Bitcoin institutional demand remains strong per on-chain data despite retail absence, suggesting potential support at current levels.",
      "Bond yields rising on failed peace talks increases stress on duration-sensitive assets and growth stocks."
    ]
